&lt;p&gt;Fortastra builds maneuverable, resilient, next-generation spacecraft that protect national security assets in orbit. We develop advanced flight systems, autonomous capabilities, and mission services that ensure U.S. and allied freedom of action in space. As we scale production and field critical defensive systems, we are looking for a Vice President of Product who can integrate technical vision, customer needs, and national-level policy to shape the future of space security.&lt;/p&gt;
