&lt;p&gt;This role will partner closely with hiring managers and leadership to execute recruiting strategies, build candidate pipelines, and deliver an outstanding candidate experience. You will play a key role in helping Fortastra attract top talent while supporting the continued development of recruiting processes as the company grows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate combines strong technical recruiting experience with a proactive sourcing mindset, excellent communication skills, and the ability to operate effectively in a fast-paced startup environment.&lt;/p&gt;
