&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute sourcing strategies to identify highly qualified technical and non-technical candidates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain candidate pipelines across engineering, product, operations, and business functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with hiring managers to define job requirements, interview plans, and hiring strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct candidate screening and assessment activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and manage interview scheduling and candidate communications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive an exceptional candidate experience throughout the recruiting process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track recruiting activity and provide regular pipeline updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support offer preparation and hiring process coordination&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help improve recruiting processes, systems, and best practices as the company grows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Fortastra professionally in all candidate interactions and external recruiting activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
